# This directory contains project-level Antigravity commands
#
# Add your custom commands here as markdown files:
#
# commands/
# └── my-command.md
#
# Command format:
# ---
# name: my-command
# description: "What this command does"
# ---
#
# Command instructions...
#
# See the Sigma Protocol documentation for command format details:
# https://github.com/dallionking/sigma-protocol
